comments: Jackson (LAC) makes legal contact to Cunningham's (DET) right hand that is a part of the ball, which results in the steal.
Zubac (LAC) slightly extends his arms into Joseph (DET) as he disengages and the contact is marginal.
Morris Sr. (LAC) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Cunningham (DET) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Zubac (LAC) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Grant (DET) maintains a legal pivot foot in the post after receiving the pass.
Livers (DET) makes marginal foot-to-foot contact with Morris Sr. (LAC) after release of his jump shot attempt that does not affect his ability to land.
Batum (LAC) does not signal for a timeout prior to the inbound pass.
Cunningham (DET) makes contact to Jackson's (DET) left arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Livers (DET) commits a take foul on Morris Sr. (LAC).
Jackson (LAC) advances the ball past the half-court line in under eight seconds.
